Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.47,0:00:04.17,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A racing second hand, a glittering galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:07.84,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Conan's logic is good medicine\Nfor hearts dried by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:11.18,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's case has a crazy secret\Nbehind a kidnapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:12.82,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:14.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:16.89,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:42.21,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Genta, Mitsuhiko, Ayumi, and I\Nwere playing Kick-the-Can,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:45.54,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but soon found ourselves having lunch at a restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:49.65,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}with Two-Mix vocalist, Minami Takayama{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:56.85,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She had snuck out to look for her missing partner, Shiina Nagano{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:04.79,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But at the restaurant, she was kidnapped before our very eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:11.40,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The kidnappers demanded\Nthe bag she left at the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:15.47,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's more, they demanded that {\i1}we{\i0} take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:19.81,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It appeared they were after a Two-Mix demo tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:26.32,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After taking the bag as ordered, the kidnappers contacted us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:32.76,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and said to lose the officers and have Ayumi deliver the tape alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.76,0:02:36.19,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't put Ayumi in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:38.82,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So, I devised a plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:54.71,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Good work, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:57.84,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There aren't any cops around, I hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there doesn't seem to be anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.92,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:05.45,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ready to come, like I told ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll try my hardest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} switched places?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My word...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kidnappers are after the demo tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said to have Ayumi deliver it\Nand to lose the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...so Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} switched with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why didn't you tell us you switched?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:43.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'd be most off guard if we let them think their plan worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said we couldn't let anyone know until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, now we can't locate the kidnappers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he said that these Tracking Glasses should—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:04:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this rate, Conan's gonna get all the credit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can still find their hideout and then tell the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, after we've saved Two-Mix...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Detective Boys Save the Day!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK! Let's go catch those kidnappers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you shouting about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we were saying, "Oh! We're so hungry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... We were saying, "Oh! We're so hungry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:47.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we're off to buy some food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come back quickly, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"We're so hungry! We're so hungry!\NWe're so hungry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:11.11,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As agreed, it looks like you came alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:15.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, bring the tape up to the second floor of the nearby warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your beloved Two-Mix is waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Won't be needing you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say your prayers while you still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I brought it, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks, little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who're you—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's the guy from the coffee shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he out somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No question about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:06:01.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to contact the police for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a phone booth over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:04.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:12.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1-1-9...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! That's the fire department!\NThe police is 110!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And don't you need to press this button?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:21.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:23.82,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is 110.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, Inspector Megure, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:32.56,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hello? Where'd you go, little boy? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:34.12,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you find us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:44.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was told to bring this tape here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:48.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they really questioned us\Nabout where the tape was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would they want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's save the details for after we've escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the police are on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:56.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:07:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're on their way here right now,\Nusing my Tracking Glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It homes in on this badge's transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan Edogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry before the other kidnapper comes back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:21.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are those your "Tracking Glasses"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I caught 'em snooping around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiots! Why didn't you give the glasses to the police?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:37.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:40.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll have plenty of time to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm nice enough to turn you into ashes. Be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! At least tell us why you kidnapped us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ask Buddha in the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The countdown bell sounds..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"and says to change hearts and run."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It rings once, twice..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:18.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Like the sound of off-season fireworks..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Like the sound of someone, somewhere, confessing their love..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You damn kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:27.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. The lyrics on the Two-Mix demo tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the reason you kidnapped Two-Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:35.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Satoshi Miyahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The night of New Year's Eve,\Nyou killed a man near Shoenji Temple
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and were investigated by Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,New Year's Eve?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:47.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shoenji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's where we came up with that song!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a murder near that temple\Nwhen the bell rang at 11:50...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the man died holding the gun,\Nhad gunpowder on his hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and there was an empty shell in the barrel,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:19.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the police believed your claim\Nthat it went off during your struggle
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with the gun-toting maniac.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that wasn't actually the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had brought the gun\Nto kill him from the very start!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After shooting him through the heart with the first shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you loaded another bullet into the barrel and fired at the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with his hand on the gun, to leave behind traces of gunpowder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were no witnesses around, so while you called the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the man sleeping outside was to run off\Nwith the extra bullet and shell
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to put you in the clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there were people who heard those sounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:08.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You two from Two-Mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "countdown bell" was the New Year's bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:14.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two fireworks were the two gunshots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the line, "1996 just flew right by,"\Nindicated the year it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Add in Shoenji Temple,\Nwhich you mentioned on the radio,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:29.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the time and place\Nof the gunshots becomes clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I assume you heard the radio show the demo tape was played on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:37.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you kidnapped Two-Mix...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to get rid of the tape and them before the police found out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm Satoshi Miyahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:11:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy I killed was an old bank-robbing partner of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He suddenly threatened\Nto tell the cops, so I offed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you have just run off after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:10.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:17.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A temple priest had seen my face while I was on my way there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luckily, he was hard of hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Said he had to stay at the temple to ring the bell, so I let him live.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never expected someone to hear the shots and make a song about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A cell phone, huh? Give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is that long-haired guy's phone\NI had my partner hold onto...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, can't be careless around you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, even if you did call the police,\Nyou'd die before they get here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:58.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, please enjoy your stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:12.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Inspector Megure. I let them and those kids go unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:15.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:20.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's odd. He didn't even mention Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} switching places...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector. I just got word on the radio
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:28.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that some kids had called 110 and asked for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:30.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! When?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:33.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, some 15 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't they tell us sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:40.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They didn't state their emergency,\Nso the operator thought it was a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:42.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do we know the location?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was too short to trace...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad! If the kidnappers were the ones who hung up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use! It's not budging!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:08.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}OK! Time for my Power Kick Shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:12.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:19.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ow! It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you kids OK?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:28.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is bad! At this rate, we won't survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:31.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't breathe the smoke! Get lower to the—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:41.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:46.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about a nuisance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those annoying cops...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Quit—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:57.98,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yay! We're long gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:00.64,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We're calling from a police box!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:03.15,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}See for yourself if you don't believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:05.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did they get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See! Told you this Earring Cell Phone was useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure was!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry! We can still get to the concert in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:41.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:45.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiina{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't mock me, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill each one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:57.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}- Bastard!\N- Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was awesome, Minami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:22.39,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}10 minutes later, a fire truck arrived with police cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:26.83,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and the two-man gang was put under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:32.00,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Naturally, the Detective Boys\Ngot a harsh scolding,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:36.67,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but Minami Takayama{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10}\Nstuck up for us, so we were acquitted
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:40.47,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and then we rushed to the Budokan\Nin Inspector Megure's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already 30 minutes past!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not good. The crowd's getting antsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:16:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to go change, so wait backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Backstage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We wanna introduce you to everyone later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Is Minami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} still not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez! What's she doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... Is this backstage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now! You're not allowed back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get back to your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takayama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} told us to come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:28.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Minami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK! Put the opening song on standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Someone go to the dressing rooms\Nand ask how much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, what does this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:39.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no! The song's started!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do we do?! They're not here yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:09.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop the song!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:13.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?! They'd get even madder if we did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:17.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm figuring that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:20.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, do you have this song's lyrics?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Yeah, they're in that CD case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what do you want them for...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:30.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're not gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,BREAK MY LIES
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"kakedasu senaka o oikakete mou ichido..."\N{\c}Chase after me again as I rush off
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:50.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SAVE MY HEART!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"hontou wa matteru ...dakishimete..."\N{\c}I'm actually waiting... Embrace me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ima RETURN TO LOVE...\N{\c}Now return to love
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:18:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could swear I've heard that singing voice before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't joke like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell's singing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about off-key...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it is Takayama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bad idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"tatta hito-koto" ga sunao ni iezu ni kizutsuketa yo\N{\c}It hurt that I couldn't say that one little thing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:38.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nakitai-kurai ni nukumori kono te ni motomenagara...\N{\c}as I sought this warm hand almost in tears
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,keiken fuereba yume mo\N{\c}And with every new experience
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,mujaki ni mirenaku naru-kara...\N{\c}I find it harder to dream in innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:54.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,sore de mo dokoka de kitto shinjitakute mitsumeteta...\N{\c}Even so, I searched because I still believed deep down
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,BREAK MY LIES
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:19:00.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"hitomi ni yureteru shinjitsu ni kidzuite..."\N{\c}Realize the quivering truth in my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SAVE MY HEART!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:05.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"furueru kuchibiru kuchidzukete..."\N{\c}Kiss these trembling lips
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ima RETURN TO LOVE...\N{\c}Now return to love
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,soba ni iru-toki kanjite ita no wa yowasa ja naku\N{\c}What I felt when I was with you wasn't weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,jibun ni tarinai nanika o oginau-you na yasuragi\N{\c}It was a kind of serenity that made up for something I lacked
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,daiji na mono-hodo itsuka\N{\c}The more important the person,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ushinau itami ga kowakute\N{\c}the more afraid I am to lose them
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,hitogomi no naka de hitori... kaeru basho o sagashiteta...\N{\c}All alone in the crowd, I searched for a place to return to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,BREAK MY LIES
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"kotoba ni dekinai setsunasa o ubatte..."\N{\c}Snatch away the pain I can't put into words
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:20:03.24,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}And so the Two-Mix concert that we barged into ended without a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:19:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SAVE MY HEART!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"doko ni mo ikenai ...sono mune ni..."\N{\c}I've nowhere to go... Trapped in your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ima RETURN TO LOVE...\N{\c}Now return to love
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See ya later!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:14.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:15.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:22.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what did you think of singing on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:24.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet! Just once, and you're hooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what did the little detective think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was the concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.81,0:20:40.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. It was OK, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:43.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so cheeky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:50.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, this is your dressing room?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.59,0:20:53.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Inspector! Can we help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to ask when you're so exhausted,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I was hoping you could come to the station to give a statement...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay. Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, take your time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a wonderful concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is for saving us today! Practice at home, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And some for you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could I get autographs and pictures, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.30,0:21:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:37.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ready?! What's 1 plus 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.39,0:23:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Karaoke Box"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all he's been singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.02,0:23:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he hasn't gotten any better...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.84,0:23:42.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Return to love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.41,0:23:48.75,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The old man was staying at the hospital,\Nbut just when he woke up,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.75,0:23:53.36,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}he witnessed a murder in the opposite ward\Nand rushed to the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.36,0:23:54.66,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.66,0:23:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Old man! Dr. Eto!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.36,0:24:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dr. Eto's murderer was you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.10,0:24:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.37,0:24:08.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No! The old man fell into a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.45,0:24:14.49,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.49,0:24:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.86,0:24:21.76,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time the stage is a scary hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.76,0:24:23.76,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I hate getting shots!
